{"tid":255214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男人搭港鐵返工可憐？ 金融才俊：踩單車更環保","createTime":"2017-05-23T17:53:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T06:05:59.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"886a786a66074b544a1f5890ab1bf6cbfba1288b","tid":255214,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T17:53:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w3z_1w1I8b8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dw3z_1w1I8b8&d=u8WlpgPihxyMZGT20wMdJv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=f994cfb0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w3z_1w1I8b8</a><br />\n發佈日期：2017年5月23日<br />\n相關連結:<br />\n<br />\n【中環無車位塞爆】美利道封場 附近車場職員：你早啲返工排隊啦！<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2qGV7AA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2qGV7AA&d=u8WlpgPihxyMZGT20wMdJv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=e75bb1f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2qGV7AA</a><br />\n_______________________<br />\n《壹週刊》周二頭條 :<br />\n【俾個叻你】無障礙的士大比拼 邊間有五星級服務咁勁?<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2qbHp5a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2qbHp5a&d=u8WlpgPihxyMZGT20wMdJv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0e3edc7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2qbHp5a</a><br />\n<br />\n《壹週刊》周二娛頭 :<br />\n【拍賣后冠勞心腦瘤復發】李珊珊高燒休克 再call白車入院<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2q3bjNO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2q3bjNO&d=u8WlpgPihxyMZGT20wMdJv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=e7c513a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2q3bjNO</a><br />\n<br />\n不少人印象，駕名車上班是金融財俊身份象徵之一，網上更有指在年過三十的男士還要依靠公共交通工具上班「好可憐」。但於中國大陸最大的民營綜合企業控股公司之一復星（656）旗下復星資本，擔任執行總經理的葉浩文（Kirk)直指：「點解要介意？」<br />\n<br />\n「我諗我出入中環，都係比較少揸車，的士或者地鐵方便好多。」葉就指，由於中環難泊車問題一直存在，他早已放棄駕駛私家車上班：「尤其係lunch time同收工，大家都知道過海又塞車，同埋中環周邊都係較難泊車。」<br />\n<br />\n葉浩文坦言「聽到要喺中環泊車都怕」，指公司附近的美利道停車場終止營運，對他沒有影響：「我自己係比較怕搵位嘅人，而且我覺得為環保，更加要使用多啲公共交通工具，如果可以踩單車更加好。」<br />\n<br />\n撰文：梁延宇<br />\n攝錄：關永浩"},{"pid":"d4b1a706bf22c5a7a77bccd8e9f6b03db8aa236b","tid":255214,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T18:18:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94dff33bcc35769c4f641d7efce8f024ff4d3263","tid":255214,"uid":100442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T18:19:04.000Z","msg":"踩單車過海"},{"pid":"e9decfefc64fd961737bda976b60e6bd7463432d","tid":255214,"uid":22095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T19:29:39.000Z","msg":"由沙田踩單車到中環  爽到加零一"},{"pid":"392aea1dd52503a78521cb3b5926c1cdfc6e370d","tid":255214,"uid":105552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T19:53:39.000Z","msg":"佢講野之前有無用腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244fc1390f14ea122733fd17a85169d084e7de91","tid":255214,"uid":61506,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T20:00:27.000Z","msg":"佢鼓勵坐公共交通工具wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好先係踩單車<br />\n做咩起哂鋼"},{"pid":"a1061fc06912a15ad0dec8acccc400513de86e4a","tid":255214,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T23:03:33.000Z","msg":"不如住埋在公司 咪唔洗周圍走"},{"pid":"3b5866a3f4dda04777e0f28eb5e9510d7c831dc2","tid":255214,"uid":17322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T23:17:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5bca962e678d5014e7ca62b912253b9d6c2a5d5a","tid":255214,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T23:22:20.000Z","msg":"我夠想同區返工啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現實上香港地有幾多人唔使跨區返工架？"},{"pid":"e588f15bc540ace2213f9e808d20ce4f832aa8fa","tid":255214,"uid":3080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T23:33:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢鼓勵坐公共交通工具wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好先係踩單車<br />\n做咩起哂鋼</blockquote><br />\n但係佢自己過海翻工，平時肯撚定唔係踩單車翻工<br />\n<br />\n自己做唔到又要強加人地身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢話如果可以嘅話踩單車仲好<br />\n俾個建議啫,點樣強加人地身上法啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4b823493b43cd0a5932955405ca342ae5cc5704","tid":255214,"uid":58889,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T23:48:54.000Z","msg":"佢講嘅野無問題喎<br />\n香港咁細 其實踩單車做交通係一流<br />\n可惜發展嘅時候唔係向呢個方向<br />\n而現在嘅規劃更加係戇鳩<br />\n所以都係坐公共交通工具啦"},{"pid":"111c3da15a4a7874ea9e0e6282c41131e95d6b32","tid":255214,"uid":20414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T23:49:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢鼓勵坐公共交通工具wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好先係踩單車<br />\n做咩起哂鋼</blockquote><br />\n但係佢自己過海翻工，平時肯撚定唔係踩單車翻工<br />\n<br />\n自己做唔到又要強加人地身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢話如果可以嘅話踩單車仲好<br />\n俾個建議啫,點樣強加人地身上法啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nd人惡到痴鳩左線，定唔識中文<br />\n<br />\n第一個［建議］，如果做到就［做更好既建議］<br />\n<br />\n咁都可以狂屌人"},{"pid":"6ea08d362c60d2d2c8f10d545f6b4646d5f3136e","tid":255214,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T00:35:19.000Z","msg":"香港啲office連基本淋浴設施都無點踩返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c608d8c75fdfafe3c549513293060786bc72dac8","tid":255214,"uid":51594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T00:36:23.000Z","msg":"今日有冇踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c76ebd2ac2f8aeb9d76d3e5160706c4b5ccc7906","tid":255214,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T00:41:47.000Z","msg":"有錢坐地鐵 =有品味<br />\n無錢坐地鐵 =痴漢"},{"pid":"ee07e13576c69cb312e332afa618db72bb42b3a9","tid":255214,"uid":64576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T00:45:56.000Z","msg":"邊到有講佢住九龍新界？"},{"pid":"7546